dora (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian release.
  * DHCPv4 server implementation with tokio async runtime
  * Duplicate address detection with ping support
  * Multiple interface binding capability
  * Static address assignments
  * Client classes for conditional configuration
  * Dynamic DNS (DDNS) updates
  * Prometheus metrics endpoint
  * HTTP API for leases and configuration management
  * SQLite backend for lease persistence
  * JSON/YAML configuration format support
  * RFC 2131/2132 compliance
  * Support for DHCP options and relay agents
  * Configurable lease times and address pools
  * Logging with tracing framework

 -- Dora DHCP developers <dora@example.com>  Tue, 12 Nov 2025 16:20:00 +0000
